iousconstantly.tumblr.com/post/182923568855/can-all-the-lesbians-on-my-dash-just-hand-the\" class=\"tumblr_blog\">anxiousconstantly</a>:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://what-even-is-thiss.tumblr.com/post/182923482515/can-all-the-lesbians-on-my-dash-just-hand-the\" class=\"tumblr_blog\">what-even-is-thiss</a>:</p>\n\n<blockquote><p>Can all the lesbians on my dash just hand the pretty girl a shiny rock or something already? I’m worried about you guys.</p></blockquote>\n\n<p>S c a r y </p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>You go out there and claim your happy ending right now young lady. Grab it by the horns.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>Pretty girls with horns???</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>Nope, no, it’s… it’s an expression. </p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>I want a pretty girl with horns…</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>I’ve decided to not make motivational posts directed at lesbians anymore.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>That’s fair.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>Wait but is there a pretty girl with horns?</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>This post is over, lesbians. Go home.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>🥺🥺🥺</p>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"what-even-is-thiss","active":true,"theme":{"header_full_width":864,"header_full_height":668,"header_focus_width":864,"header_focus_height":486,"avatar_shape":"square","background_color":"#FAFAFA","body_font":"Helvetica Neue","header_bounds":"136,864,622,0","header_image":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/a5986166f0e56e33e3184af5755d2220/1801a3ec7c497ef0-11/s864x668/3b31d67c3dfee237f327896f01433c43f7738940.png","header_image_focused":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/a5986166f0e56e33e3184af5755d2220/1801a3ec7c497ef0-11/s2048x3072_c0,20359,100000,93114/40922202bcdd620c7ce747dfee29a2757748f971.png","header_image_poster":"","header_image_scaled":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/a5986166f0e56e33e3184af5755d2220/1801a3ec7c497ef0-11/s2048x3072/1968c49d4f6b354d77d02264545ab633d554bb89.png","header_stretch":true,"link_color":"#A77DC2","show_avatar":true,"show_description":true,"show_header_image":tr